import { Box, Button, Heading, Stack, useBreakpoint, useBreakpointValue } from '@chakra-ui/react'
import React from 'react'

export const Class = () => {
    const text = useBreakpointValue( {
        base:'basic',
        sm:"small",
        md:"medium"
     })
   
  return (
    

    <Box>
        <Flex>
              <Heading>DermaStore</Heading>
        
        </Flex>
     
        <Box>

        
        <Stack direction={{base:'column',md:"row"}}>
          
          <Button>{text}</Button>
          <Button>Hello</Button>

          <Button>World </Button>

        </Stack>
        </Box>



    </Box>
  )
}
